《'''夜'''》（{{lang-it|''La Notte''}}，{{lang-en|''The Night''}})）是一部1961年意大利导演[[米开朗基罗·安东尼奥尼|米开朗基罗·安东尼奥尼]]执导的黑白剧情片，[[馬切洛·馬斯楚安尼|馬切洛·馬斯楚安尼]]、[[珍妮·摩露|珍妮·摩露]]和{{le|莫尼卡·维蒂|Monica Vitti}}主演<ref name="IMDb">{{cite web |title=La Notte |publisher=''Internet Movie Database'' |url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0054130/ |accessdate=8 March 2012 |archive-date=2021-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204160636/https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0054130/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。影片获得第11届[[柏林影展|柏林影展]][[金熊奖|金熊奖]]，安东尼奥尼赢得[[意大利电影金像奖|意大利电影金像奖]]最佳导演奖。本片与1960年的《[[情事_(意大利電影)|情事]]》和1962年的《[[欲海含羞花|欲海含羞花]]》并列视为“疏离（爱情）三部曲”<ref name="gazetas">{{cite book |last=Gazetas |first=Aristides |title=An Introduction to World Cinema |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=CPuZ-2UtVRwC&pg=PA246 |accessdate=31 May 2011 |year=2008 |publisher=McFarland |isbn=978-0-7864-3907-2 |page=246 |archive-date=2017-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170227064559/https://books.google.com/books?id=CPuZ-2UtVRwC&pg=PA246 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="wakeman">{{cite book |last=Wakeman |first=John |title=World Film Directors: 1945–1985 |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=8aEYAAAAIAAJ |accessdate=31 May 2011 |year=1988 |publisher=H. W. Wilson |page=65 |archive-date=2020-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101144101/https://books.google.com/books?id=8aEYAAAAIAAJ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="cameron">{{cite book |last1=Cameron |first1=Ian Alexander |last2=Wood |first2=Robin |title=Antonioni |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=PXhZAAAAMAAJ |accessdate=31 May 2011 |year=1971 |publisher=Praeger |page=105 |archive-date=2016-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160611031415/https://books.google.com/books?id=PXhZAAAAMAAJ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==剧情==
